name: ioquake3
caveats:
To complete the installation of ioquake3, you will have to copy the file 'pak0.pk3' from your Quake 3 Arena installation support directory into

/Applications/ioquake3/baseq3/ or ~/Library/Application Support/Quake3/baseq3/

and download patch data from https://files.ioquake3.org/quake3-latest-pk3s.zip
